title: 155: The Trader Joe’s Haul for the Holidays Episode
itunes:title: The Trader Joe’s Haul for the Holidays Episode
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa and the gang are trying over a dozen incredibly tasty holiday finds from Trader Joe’s! Finds like pumpkin spice hummus, dry-roasted maple almonds, maple walnut biscotti, 4-cheese pumpkin yogurt dip, pumpkin spice espresso beans, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, the find of all finds that will change your breakfast toast forever! So STOP EVERYTHING, push play, and then head on over to our Foodcast page for the list of items mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: TJ’s has so many great holiday finds, we HAD to do an entire episode on them!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
dc:creator: Lisa Lillien
